_sText:
This is FY_GG_MODERNBATTLE, it is my most porzed map i have made!
The map can be used for Fightyard battle and a gungame match.
The style is a new original scene, something that i have never seen before in a map.

There are several buildings, 4 to be exact and they all have that modern time of look to them. The two buildings in the middle have a modern looking bridge linking them. Below there is a fighting platform witch also links across the water. There are ladders for climing to the top of these buildings and plaTforms.
As you can see there are also 4 baracades for people to fight behind they alos have a modern look to them.
But that not all, i was in the precess (before starting this map) of making an underground hostage bunker map with my own textures, but that project fell through. So when i finished making this map i thought i would add what i was making into it. SO now this map has under ground bunker with the theme from cs_office. (if you are getting texture errors dont worry about then it just means i mist changing some the textures on the outsite oft he map, bits you cant see)

Please watch the youtube video and tell me what you think, like what i can improve on and thing that i may be able to had or take away.
